azzling skill with genuine humility, solving problems at a speed others struggle to follow."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"naruto","result_name":"Naruto Uzumaki","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Naruto Uzumaki","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Unbreakable Heart","key":"naruto","description":"You lead with pure heart and refuse to quit, no matter how long the odds."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"neji","result_name":"Neji Hyuga","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Neji Hyuga","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Sharpened Pride","key":"neji","description":"You hold yourself and everyone around you to exacting standards, with the skill to back it up."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"obito","result_name":"Obito Uchiha","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Obito Uchiha","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Man Behind the Mask","key":"obito","description":"You move through the world behind a mask, letting people see only what serves your design."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"orochimaru","result_name":"Orochimaru","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Orochimaru","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Endless Seeker","key":"orochimaru","description":"You're driven by an insatiable hunger to know and to slip past every limit set in front of you."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"pain","result_name":"Pain (Nagato)","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Pain (Nagato)","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Voice of Pain","key":"pain","description":"You carry a grand vision and the cold conviction to see it through."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"sasori","result_name":"Sasori","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Sasori","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Timeless Craftsman","key":"sasori","description":"You believe true art lasts forever, and you build with patience most people can't summon."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"sasuke","result_name":"Sasuke Uchiha","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Sasuke Uchiha","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Lone Blade","key":"sasuke","description":"You carry your goals alone and hold yourself to a standard almost nobody else can see."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"shikamaru","result_name":"Shikamaru Nara","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Shikamaru Nara","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Ten-Move Mind","key":"shikamaru","description":"You conserve energy for what matters and solve problems in your head before anyone notices there was one."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"tobirama","result_name":"Tobirama Senju","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Tobirama Senju","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Cold Current","key":"tobirama","description":"You approach every problem with a cool, analytical mind and say the hard truths out loud."}},{"quiz_type":"naruto","result_key":"tsunade","result_name":"Tsunade","result_emoji":"🍥","result_data":{"name":"Tsunade","emoji":"🍥","tagline":"The Healing Fist","key":"tsunade","description":"You lead with raw strength and an even bigger sense of duty to the people under you."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"barkley","result_name":"Charles Barkley","result_emoji":"💪","result_data":{"name":"Charles Barkley","emoji":"💪","tagline":"The Unfiltered Force","key":"barkley","description":"You say exactly what you think, you back it up with everything you have, and you refuse to be anybody but yourself."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"big_ben","result_name":"Ben Wallace","result_emoji":"🔔","result_data":{"name":"Ben Wallace","emoji":"🔔","tagline":"The Blue-Collar Wall","key":"big_ben","description":"Nobody drafted you, nobody hyped you, and you built a fortress out of that silence."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"bird","result_name":"Larry Bird","result_emoji":"🍀","result_data":{"name":"Larry Bird","emoji":"🍀","tagline":"The Stone-Faced Sniper","key":"bird","description":"You'll tell the room exactly what you're about to do, do it, and walk away without changing expression."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"curry","result_name":"Stephen Curry","result_emoji":"🎯","result_data":{"name":"Stephen Curry","emoji":"🎯","tagline":"The Joyful Revolution","key":"curry","description":"They said you were too small, too light, too far from the target — so you changed what everyone considers possible and grinned the whole way."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"dirk","result_name":"Dirk Nowitzki","result_emoji":"🦩","result_data":{"name":"Dirk Nowitzki","emoji":"🦩","tagline":"The Faithful Fadeaway","key":"dirk","description":"You built one unguardable thing through years of strange, patient practice, and you stayed loyal to one place while the whole world told you to chase shortcuts."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"drj","result_name":"Julius Erving","result_emoji":"🩺","result_data":{"name":"Julius Erving","emoji":"🩺","tagline":"The Doctor of Flight","key":"drj","description":"You do difficult things with such elegance that people forget how difficult they are."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"duncan","result_name":"Tim Duncan","result_emoji":"🗿","result_data":{"name":"Tim Duncan","emoji":"🗿","tagline":"The Quiet Fundamental","key":"duncan","description":"You are the steadiest person anyone knows, and you've made steadiness an art form."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"garnett","result_name":"Kevin Garnett","result_emoji":"🐺","result_data":{"name":"Kevin Garnett","emoji":"🐺","tagline":"The Blazing Heartbeat","key":"garnett","description":"You feel everything at maximum volume — the wins, the losses, the pride of the crest on your chest."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"hakeem","result_name":"Hakeem Olajuwon","result_emoji":"💫","result_data":{"name":"Hakeem Olajuwon","emoji":"💫","tagline":"The Gentle Dream","key":"hakeem","description":"You move through hard problems the way a dancer moves through a routine — with footwork, patience, and a grace nobody can quite copy."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"iverson","result_name":"Allen Iverson","result_emoji":"💥","result_data":{"name":"Allen Iverson","emoji":"💥","tagline":"The Crossover Heart","key":"iverson","description":"Nobody has ever successfully told you who to be, and it's far too late to start now."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"jordan","result_name":"Michael Jordan","result_emoji":"🐐","result_data":{"name":"Michael Jordan","emoji":"🐐","tagline":"The Last Shot","key":"jordan","description":"You live for the moment everyone else is trying to survive."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"kareem","result_name":"Kareem Abdul-Jabbar","result_emoji":"🪝","result_data":{"name":"Kareem Abdul-Jabbar","emoji":"🪝","tagline":"The Scholar's Skyhook","key":"kareem","description":"You found one perfect thing, refined it for decades, and let mastery speak while everyone else shouted."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"kobe","result_name":"Kobe Bryant","result_emoji":"🐍","result_data":{"name":"Kobe Bryant","emoji":"🐍","tagline":"The 4 A.M. Craftsman","key":"kobe","description":"You're in love with the work itself — the empty gym, the extra rep, the detail nobody else even knows exists."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"lebron","result_name":"LeBron James","result_emoji":"👑","result_data":{"name":"LeBron James","emoji":"👑","tagline":"The Empire Builder","key":"lebron","description":"You're somehow the most capable person in the room and the most invested in everyone else's rise."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"magic","result_name":"Magic Johnson","result_emoji":"✨","result_data":{"name":"Magic Johnson","emoji":"✨","tagline":"The Showtime Smile","key":"magic","description":"Your superpower is making other people shine and loving it more than your own spotlight."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"manu","result_name":"Manu Ginóbili","result_emoji":"🦇","result_data":{"name":"Manu Ginóbili","emoji":"🦇","tagline":"The Daring Sixth Man","key":"manu","description":"You accepted a smaller title so the whole team could be bigger, then played like the boldest person on the floor anyway."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"muggsy","result_name":"Muggsy Bogues","result_emoji":"🐝","result_data":{"name":"Muggsy Bogues","emoji":"🐝","tagline":"The Tallest Heart","key":"muggsy","description":"Every room you've ever entered underestimated you, and you've spent a lifetime cheerfully proving every single one of them wrong."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"nash","result_name":"Steve Nash","result_emoji":"🪄","result_data":{"name":"Steve Nash","emoji":"🪄","tagline":"The Smiling Conductor","key":"nash","description":"You make everyone around you play — and feel — better than they thought they could."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"pistol","result_name":"Pete Maravich","result_emoji":"🧦","result_data":{"name":"Pete Maravich","emoji":"🧦","tagline":"The Floppy-Socked Wizard","key":"pistol","description":"You practiced magic tricks until they became fundamentals, then unveiled them when the world least expected it."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"reggie","result_name":"Reggie Miller","result_emoji":"🏹","result_data":{"name":"Reggie Miller","emoji":"🏹","tagline":"The Road-Game Villain","key":"reggie","description":"You're at your very best when the entire building wants you to fail."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"rodman","result_name":"Dennis Rodman","result_emoji":"🌈","result_data":{"name":"Dennis Rodman","emoji":"🌈","tagline":"The Beautiful Chaos","key":"rodman","description":"You do the work nobody else wants — the diving, the scrapping, the fiftieth effort — and you do it dressed exactly how you please."}},{"quiz_type":"nba","result_key":"shaq","result_name":"Shaquille O'Neal","result_emoji":"🌋","result_data":{"name":"Shaquille O'Neal","emoji":"🌋","tagline":"The Playful Colossus","key":"shaq","description":"You're overwhelming force and pure comedy in one enormous package, and nobody has ever figured out how to handle both at once."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"andy","result_name":"Andy Bernard","result_emoji":"🎶","result_data":{"name":"Andy Bernard","emoji":"🎶","tagline":"The Eager Crescendo","key":"andy","description":"You want so badly to be liked that you've turned it into a genuine art form — the song, the nickname, the grand gesture, whatever the moment demands."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"angela","result_name":"Angela Martin","result_emoji":"🐱","result_data":{"name":"Angela Martin","emoji":"🐱","tagline":"The Iron Standard","key":"angela","description":"You have standards, a plan, and a committee ready to execute both, and you are not sorry about any of it."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"creed","result_name":"Creed Bratton","result_emoji":"🌱","result_data":{"name":"Creed Bratton","emoji":"🌱","tagline":"The Unknowable Wildcard","key":"creed","description":"Nobody knows exactly what you do, where you came from, or how you got into the building, and you have decided to keep it that way."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"darryl","result_name":"Darryl Philbin","result_emoji":"🎧","result_data":{"name":"Darryl Philbin","emoji":"🎧","tagline":"The Understated Climber","key":"darryl","description":"You're the calmest, most capable person on the floor, and you've perfected the art of being underestimated on purpose."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"dwight","result_name":"Dwight Schrute","result_emoji":"🌾","result_data":{"name":"Dwight Schrute","emoji":"🌾","tagline":"The Relentless Sentinel","key":"dwight","description":"You are intense about everything, prepared for anything, and completely unbothered that people find both of those things strange."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"erin","result_name":"Erin Hannon","result_emoji":"☀️","result_data":{"name":"Erin Hannon","emoji":"☀️","tagline":"The Unsinkable Sunbeam","key":"erin","description":"You bring a sincerity so bright that cynics need a moment to adjust their eyes."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"jan","result_name":"Jan Levinson","result_emoji":"🕯️","result_data":{"name":"Jan Levinson","emoji":"🕯️","tagline":"The Scorched-Earth Striver","key":"jan","description":"You climbed higher than anyone around you, held yourself to a punishing standard, and discovered the polished exterior was the least interesting thing about you."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"jim","result_name":"Jim Halpert","result_emoji":"😏","result_data":{"name":"Jim Halpert","emoji":"😏","tagline":"The Smirking Long Game","key":"jim","description":"You glide through chaos with a raised eyebrow and a private joke, and people trust you precisely because you refuse to take any of it too seriously."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"kelly","result_name":"Kelly Kapoor","result_emoji":"💅","result_data":{"name":"Kelly Kapoor","emoji":"💅","tagline":"The Main Character","key":"kelly","description":"You are the main character, and honestly, everyone should thank you for it."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"kevin","result_name":"Kevin Malone","result_emoji":"🍪","result_data":{"name":"Kevin Malone","emoji":"🍪","tagline":"The Uncomplicated Heart","key":"kevin","description":"You cracked the code to happiness, and the code is beautifully simple: good food, good people, and a firm policy against sweating the small stuff."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"michael","result_name":"Michael Scott","result_emoji":"🎤","result_data":{"name":"Michael Scott","emoji":"🎤","tagline":"The Showtime Heart","key":"michael","description":"You love the people around you at a volume most reserve for weddings and playoff games, and you'd rather be their favorite person than their boss — even when you're literally their boss."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"oscar","result_name":"Oscar Martinez","result_emoji":"🧮","result_data":{"name":"Oscar Martinez","emoji":"🧮","tagline":"The Voice of Reason","key":"oscar","description":"You're usually the smartest person in the room and, to your credit, you only mention it several times a day."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"pam","result_name":"Pam Beesly","result_emoji":"🎨","result_data":{"name":"Pam Beesly","emoji":"🎨","tagline":"The Quiet Courage","key":"pam","description":"You notice everything, say a tenth of it, and quietly keep the whole ecosystem running while louder people take the credit."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"phyllis","result_name":"Phyllis Vance","result_emoji":"🧶","result_data":{"name":"Phyllis Vance","emoji":"🧶","tagline":"The Velvet Needle","key":"phyllis","description":"You look like the sweetest person in the building, and you are — but the people who mistake sweet for soft learn otherwise exactly once."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"ryan","result_name":"Ryan Howard","result_emoji":"📱","result_data":{"name":"Ryan Howard","emoji":"📱","tagline":"The Restless Hustler","key":"ryan","description":"You've reinvented yourself more times than most people update their résumé, and every version is chasing something bigger."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"stanley","result_name":"Stanley Hudson","result_emoji":"🧩","result_data":{"name":"Stanley Hudson","emoji":"🧩","tagline":"The Fortress of Peace","key":"stanley","description":"You solved the puzzle most people spend decades on: work is one chapter of your life, not the whole book."}},{"quiz_type":"office","result_key":"toby","result_name":"Toby Flenderson","result_emoji":"📋","result_data":{"name":"Toby Flenderson","emoji":"📋","tagline":"The Quiet Endurance","key":"toby","description":"You follow the rules, file the forms, and absorb an astonishing amount of unearned hostility with a patience that borders on heroic."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"ace","result_name":"Portgas D. Ace","result_emoji":"🔥","result_data":{"name":"Portgas D. Ace","emoji":"🔥","tagline":"The Blazing Big Brother","key":"ace","description":"You burn hot and love harder, wearing every feeling right there on your sleeve."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"brook","result_name":"Brook","result_emoji":"🎻","result_data":{"name":"Brook","emoji":"🎻","tagline":"The Soul of the Party","key":"brook","description":"You've decided that joy is a discipline, and you practice it louder than anyone."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"buggy","result_name":"Buggy","result_emoji":"🤡","result_data":{"name":"Buggy","emoji":"🤡","tagline":"The Accidental Legend","key":"buggy","description":"You're a showman first, a schemer second, and — to your own eternal surprise — a legend third."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"chopper","result_name":"Tony Tony Chopper","result_emoji":"🩺","result_data":{"name":"Tony Tony Chopper","emoji":"🩺","tagline":"The Cotton-Candy Heart","key":"chopper","description":"You lead with kindness in a world that doesn't always deserve it, and you refuse to let that change you."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"franky","result_name":"Franky","result_emoji":"🔧","result_data":{"name":"Franky","emoji":"🔧","tagline":"The Roaring Blueprint","key":"franky","description":"You're maximum volume, maximum heart, and maximum output, usually all at once."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"garp","result_name":"Monkey D. Garp","result_emoji":"👊","result_data":{"name":"Monkey D. Garp","emoji":"👊","tagline":"The Fist of Love","key":"garp","description":"You're a legend who refuses to act like one, laughing through meetings, napping through ceremonies, and solving problems with alarming directness."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"hancock","result_name":"Boa Hancock","result_emoji":"🐍","result_data":{"name":"Boa Hancock","emoji":"🐍","tagline":"The Proud Empress","key":"hancock","description":"You move through the world like it should be grateful for the view, and honestly, your confidence does most of the work."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"jinbe","result_name":"Jinbe","result_emoji":"🌊","result_data":{"name":"Jinbe","emoji":"🌊","tagline":"The Steady Helmsman","key":"jinbe","description":"You're the steady hand people reach for when the water turns rough."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"katakuri","result_name":"Charlotte Katakuri","result_emoji":"🍡","result_data":{"name":"Charlotte Katakuri","emoji":"🍡","tagline":"The Flawless Guardian","key":"katakuri","description":"You've built a reputation for being flawless, and you maintain it the unglamorous way: preparation, discipline, and standards nobody ever sees you sweat for."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"law","result_name":"Trafalgar Law","result_emoji":"⚕️","result_data":{"name":"Trafalgar Law","emoji":"⚕️","tagline":"The Deadpan Surgeon","key":"law","description":"You plan thirteen steps ahead, say about six words, and let the results do the talking."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"luffy","result_name":"Monkey D. Luffy","result_emoji":"🍖","result_data":{"name":"Monkey D. Luffy","emoji":"🍖","tagline":"The Grinning Horizon","key":"luffy","description":"You move through life on appetite and instinct, and somehow the wildest route keeps turning out to be the right one."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"mihawk","result_name":"Dracule Mihawk","result_emoji":"🦅","result_data":{"name":"Dracule Mihawk","emoji":"🦅","tagline":"The Lonely Summit","key":"mihawk","description":"You climbed to the top of your craft and found it quiet up there — which suits you fine."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"nami","result_name":"Nami","result_emoji":"🍊","result_data":{"name":"Nami","emoji":"🍊","tagline":"The Storm Reader","key":"nami","description":"You're the one who actually knows where the group is going, what it will cost, and which three things could go wrong on the way."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"robin","result_name":"Nico Robin","result_emoji":"📚","result_data":{"name":"Nico Robin","emoji":"📚","tagline":"The Smiling Archive","key":"robin","description":"You're the calm, watchful one who has already read the room, the subtext, and three books on the subject."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"sabo","result_name":"Sabo","result_emoji":"🎩","result_data":{"name":"Sabo","emoji":"🎩","tagline":"The Gentleman Firebrand","key":"sabo","description":"You believe the world's rules were written badly, and you've made it your life's work to redraft them."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"sanji","result_name":"Sanji","result_emoji":"🍳","result_data":{"name":"Sanji","emoji":"🍳","tagline":"The Knight of the Kitchen","key":"sanji","description":"Your love language is looking after people — usually through food, always with flair."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"shanks","result_name":"Shanks","result_emoji":"🕊️","result_data":{"name":"Shanks","emoji":"🕊️","tagline":"The Easygoing Legend","key":"shanks","description":"You've got nothing left to prove, and it shows in how lightly you carry your strength."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"usopp","result_name":"Usopp","result_emoji":"🎯","result_data":{"name":"Usopp","emoji":"🎯","tagline":"The Trembling Sharpshooter","key":"usopp","description":"You're honest about being scared, and that's exactly what makes your courage the real kind."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"whitebeard","result_name":"Edward Newgate (Whitebeard)","result_emoji":"⚓","result_data":{"name":"Edward Newgate (Whitebeard)","emoji":"⚓","tagline":"The Father of the Seas","key":"whitebeard","description":"You gave up chasing treasure a long time ago, because you found the thing worth more: a family that calls you theirs."}},{"quiz_type":"onepiece","result_key":"zoro","result_name":"Roronoa Zoro","result_emoji":"⚔️","result_data":{"name":"Roronoa Zoro","emoji":"⚔️","tagline":"The Unbending Blade","key":"zoro","description":"You picked your mountain years ago and you've been climbing it every single day since, no announcements, no excuses."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"alakazam","result_name":"Alakazam","result_emoji":"🥄","result_data":{"name":"Alakazam","emoji":"🥄","tagline":"The Grandmaster Mind","key":"alakazam","description":"You think five conversations ahead and it shows — you rarely raise your voice because you rarely need to."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"bulbasaur","result_name":"Bulbasaur","result_emoji":"🌱","result_data":{"name":"Bulbasaur","emoji":"🌱","tagline":"The Patient Gardener","key":"bulbasaur","description":"You're the one who remembers the birthday, waters the plants, and shows up early with snacks on moving day."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"charizard","result_name":"Charizard","result_emoji":"🐉","result_data":{"name":"Charizard","emoji":"🐉","tagline":"The Proud Inferno","key":"charizard","description":"You have real power and absolutely no interest in pretending otherwise — respect is earned with you, never assumed."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"charmander","result_name":"Charmander","result_emoji":"🔥","result_data":{"name":"Charmander","emoji":"🔥","tagline":"The Rising Ember","key":"charmander","description":"You feel everything at full temperature — your enthusiasms are bonfires and your loyalties are furnace-grade."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"cyndaquil","result_name":"Cyndaquil","result_emoji":"🌋","result_data":{"name":"Cyndaquil","emoji":"🌋","tagline":"The Quiet Flame","key":"cyndaquil","description":"You're soft-spoken, a little shy, and routinely underestimated — right up until something you love is threatened and the flames come roaring to life."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"ditto","result_name":"Ditto","result_emoji":"🎭","result_data":{"name":"Ditto","emoji":"🎭","tagline":"The Perfect Impression","key":"ditto","description":"You can read a room in seconds and become exactly what the moment requires — the calm one, the funny one, the translator between two stubborn friends."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"dragonite","result_name":"Dragonite","result_emoji":"🐲","result_data":{"name":"Dragonite","emoji":"🐲","tagline":"The Kindhearted Colossus","key":"dragonite","description":"You are enormous strength wrapped around a soft center — the most powerful person in the room and somehow the friendliest."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"eevee","result_name":"Eevee","result_emoji":"🦊","result_data":{"name":"Eevee","emoji":"🦊","tagline":"The Infinite Possibility","key":"eevee","description":"You contain multitudes and you know it — while everyone else locked in their one path years ago, you kept your options gloriously open."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"gengar","result_name":"Gengar","result_emoji":"👻","result_data":{"name":"Gengar","emoji":"👻","tagline":"The Grinning Shadow","key":"gengar","description":"Your pranks are legendary, your timing is flawless, and your laugh always seems to come from just over someone's shoulder."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"gyarados","result_name":"Gyarados","result_emoji":"🌊","result_data":{"name":"Gyarados","emoji":"🌊","tagline":"The Risen Tempest","key":"gyarados","description":"People wrote you off once, and you have never forgotten how it felt — everything you are now was built from that."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"jigglypuff","result_name":"Jigglypuff","result_emoji":"🎤","result_data":{"name":"Jigglypuff","emoji":"🎤","tagline":"The Unstoppable Encore","key":"jigglypuff","description":"You were born for the spotlight and genuinely cannot understand why anyone would fall asleep during your set."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"lapras","result_name":"Lapras","result_emoji":"⛵","result_data":{"name":"Lapras","emoji":"⛵","tagline":"The Calm-Water Carrier","key":"lapras","description":"You're the calm crossing in other people's stormy seasons — patient, unhurried, and quietly wise."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"lucario","result_name":"Lucario","result_emoji":"🥋","result_data":{"name":"Lucario","emoji":"🥋","tagline":"The Focused Aura","key":"lucario","description":"You sense what people are feeling before they've said a word, and you take that gift seriously."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"machamp","result_name":"Machamp","result_emoji":"💪","result_data":{"name":"Machamp","emoji":"💪","tagline":"The Four-Armed Work Ethic","key":"machamp","description":"You genuinely believe in the reps — show up, do the work, get stronger, repeat — and your consistency puts everyone else's motivation apps to shame."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"meowth","result_name":"Meowth","result_emoji":"🪙","result_data":{"name":"Meowth","emoji":"🪙","tagline":"The Silver-Tongued Schemer","key":"meowth","description":"You've always had an angle, a plan, and a backup plan that's mostly the first plan with more style."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"mewtwo","result_name":"Mewtwo","result_emoji":"🔮","result_data":{"name":"Mewtwo","emoji":"🔮","tagline":"The Solitary Storm","key":"mewtwo","description":"You think at a depth most people never visit and prefer to do it far from the noise."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"pikachu","result_name":"Pikachu","result_emoji":"⚡","result_data":{"name":"Pikachu","emoji":"⚡","tagline":"The Loyal Livewire","key":"pikachu","description":"Your energy enters the room a full second before you do, and it never runs out where your people are concerned."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"psyduck","result_name":"Psyduck","result_emoji":"🤯","result_data":{"name":"Psyduck","emoji":"🤯","tagline":"The Accidental Powerhouse","key":"psyduck","description":"You spend most days mildly overwhelmed, holding your head and doing your best — and your best is better than you think."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"snorlax","result_name":"Snorlax","result_emoji":"😴","result_data":{"name":"Snorlax","emoji":"😴","tagline":"The Immovable Nap","key":"snorlax","description":"You have mastered the art everyone else is still fumbling: being completely, unapologetically at peace."}},{"quiz_type":"pokemon","result_key":"squirtle","result_name":"Squirtle","result_emoji":"💧","result_data":{"name":"Squirtle","emoji":"💧","tagline":"The Squad's Cool Head","key":"squirtle","description":"You're the coolest head in any crisis and the biggest personality at any party, which makes you dangerously fun to know."}},{"quiz_type":"riasec","result_key":"artistic","result_name":"The Creator","result_emoji":"🎨","result_data":{"name":"The Creator","emoji":"🎨","color":"from-fuchsia-100 to-pink-50","accent":"text-fuchsia-600","tagline":"#BlankPageEnergy #OriginalOnly #MakeItBeautiful","key":"artistic","description":"You experience rules, templates, and dress codes as a mild form of suffocation."}},{"quiz_type":"riasec","result_key":"conventional","result_name":"The Organizer","result_emoji":"📊","result_data":{"name":"The Organizer","emoji":"📊","color":"from-emerald-100 to-teal-50","accent":"text-emerald-600","tagline":"#OrderFromChaos #DetailsMatter #TrustTheSystem","key":"conventional","description":"Where others see a boring spreadsheet, you see a small kingdom that could be ruled beautifully."}},{"quiz_type":"riasec","result_key":"enterprising","result_name":"The Persuader","result_emoji":"📣","result_data":{"name":"The Persuader","emoji":"📣","color":"from-orange-100 to-amber-50","accent":"text-orange-600","tagline":"#PitchIt #LetsGo #BetOnYourself","key":"enterprising","description":"You see opportunities the way other people see obstacles, and you cannot resist recruiting others into your vision of what could be."}},{"quiz_type":"riasec","result_key":"investigative","result_name":"The Thinker","result_emoji":"🔬","result_data":{"name":"The Thinker","emoji":"🔬","color":"from-sky-100 to-cyan-50","accent":"text-sky-700","tagline":"#WhyThough #FollowTheEvidence #DeepDive","key":"investigative","description":"Your native question is \"why?"}},{"quiz_type":"riasec","result_key":"realistic","result_name":"The Builder","result_emoji":"🔧","result_data":{"name":"The Builder","emoji":"🔧","color":"from-amber-100 to-orange-50","accent":"text-amber-700","tagline":"#HandsOn #MakeItReal #FixItYourself","key":"realistic","description":"You think with your hands."}},{"quiz_type":"riasec","result_key":"social","result_name":"The Helper","result_emoji":"🤝","result_data":{"name":"The Helper","emoji":"🤝","color":"from-rose-100 to-pink-50","accent":"text-rose-600","tagline":"#PeopleFirst #WatchThemGrow #ShowUp","key":"social","description":"For you, the most interesting system in any room is the people in it."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"baggio","result_name":"Roberto Baggio","result_emoji":"🪷","result_data":{"name":"Roberto Baggio","emoji":"🪷","tagline":"The Divine Ponytail","key":"baggio","description":"You're an artist in a results business, and you've made peace with the weight that carries."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"beckenbauer","result_name":"Franz Beckenbauer","result_emoji":"🦅","result_data":{"name":"Franz Beckenbauer","emoji":"🦅","tagline":"The Imperial Calm","key":"beckenbauer","description":"You stroll through pressure that makes other people sprint in circles."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"buffon","result_name":"Gianluigi Buffon","result_emoji":"🧤","result_data":{"name":"Gianluigi Buffon","emoji":"🧤","tagline":"The Joyful Guardian","key":"buffon","description":"You're the one everybody trusts when everything is on fire, and you genuinely love being that person."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"cantona","result_name":"Eric Cantona","result_emoji":"🎭","result_data":{"name":"Eric Cantona","emoji":"🎭","tagline":"The Collar-Up King","key":"cantona","description":"You walk into every room like you own the deed, and somehow the room agrees."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"cruyff","result_name":"Johan Cruyff","result_emoji":"🧠","result_data":{"name":"Johan Cruyff","emoji":"🧠","tagline":"The Total Visionary","key":"cruyff","description":"You don't just play the game — you redesign it while everyone else is still learning the rules."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"gattuso","result_name":"Gennaro Gattuso","result_emoji":"⚒️","result_data":{"name":"Gennaro Gattuso","emoji":"⚒️","tagline":"The Snarling Heartbeat","key":"gattuso","description":"You're the teammate people want beside them when everything goes wrong."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"higuita","result_name":"René Higuita","result_emoji":"🦂","result_data":{"name":"René Higuita","emoji":"🦂","tagline":"The Scorpion Gambler","key":"higuita","description":"Where everyone else sees a rule, you see a suggestion — and probably an opportunity."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"maldini","result_name":"Paolo Maldini","result_emoji":"🛡️","result_data":{"name":"Paolo Maldini","emoji":"🛡️","tagline":"The Elegant Wall","key":"maldini","description":"You've turned defending — of people, of standards, of places — into an art form."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"maradona","result_name":"Diego Maradona","result_emoji":"🔟","result_data":{"name":"Diego Maradona","emoji":"🔟","tagline":"The Impossible No. 10","key":"maradona","description":"You carry whole causes on your shoulders and somehow make the impossible feel inevitable."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"marta","result_name":"Marta","result_emoji":"🔥","result_data":{"name":"Marta","emoji":"🔥","tagline":"The Trailblazing Flame","key":"marta","description":"You didn't find a path — you cut one, straight through terrain everyone said was closed to people like you."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"mbappe","result_name":"Kylian Mbappé","result_emoji":"⚡","result_data":{"name":"Kylian Mbappé","emoji":"⚡","tagline":"The Fast Forward","key":"mbappe","description":"You have never once waited your turn."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"messi","result_name":"Lionel Messi","result_emoji":"🐐","result_data":{"name":"Lionel Messi","emoji":"🐐","tagline":"The Quiet Genius","key":"messi","description":"You're the quietest person in the room and somehow the one everyone watches."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"modric","result_name":"Luka Modrić","result_emoji":"🧭","result_data":{"name":"Luka Modrić","emoji":"🧭","tagline":"The Midfield Metronome","key":"modric","description":"They said you were too small, too slight, too quiet for the top level — so you simply kept going until the doubters ran out of arguments."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"pele","result_name":"Pelé","result_emoji":"👑","result_data":{"name":"Pelé","emoji":"👑","tagline":"The Smiling King","key":"pele","description":"You make excellence look like celebration — greatness delivered with a grin and shared with everyone around you."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"puyol","result_name":"Carles Puyol","result_emoji":"🦁","result_data":{"name":"Carles Puyol","emoji":"🦁","tagline":"The Lionhearted Captain","key":"puyol","description":"You'd throw yourself in front of anything for your people, and they know it without you ever saying so."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"r9","result_name":"Ronaldo Nazário","result_emoji":"💥","result_data":{"name":"Ronaldo Nazário","emoji":"💥","tagline":"The Original Phenomenon","key":"r9","description":"You have a gift so natural it looks like it was waiting for you to be born."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"rapinoe","result_name":"Megan Rapinoe","result_emoji":"🎤","result_data":{"name":"Megan Rapinoe","emoji":"🎤","tagline":"The Fearless Showstopper","key":"rapinoe","description":"You show up loudest exactly when it's riskiest — the biggest stage, the tensest moment, the conversation everyone else avoids."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"ronaldinho","result_name":"Ronaldinho","result_emoji":"😁","result_data":{"name":"Ronaldinho","emoji":"😁","tagline":"The Laughing Magician","key":"ronaldinho","description":"You're living proof that excellence and fun are dance partners, not opposites."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"ronaldo","result_name":"Cristiano Ronaldo","result_emoji":"🚀","result_data":{"name":"Cristiano Ronaldo","emoji":"🚀","tagline":"The Relentless Standard","key":"ronaldo","description":"You decided long ago exactly who you were going to become, and you've been out-working everyone toward it ever since."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"socrates","result_name":"Sócrates","result_emoji":"🩺","result_data":{"name":"Sócrates","emoji":"🩺","tagline":"The Bearded Philosopher","key":"socrates","description":"You play the long game — of ideas, of principle, of the collective good."}},{"quiz_type":"soccer","result_key":"zidane","result_name":"Zinedine Zidane","result_emoji":"🎩","result_data":{"name":"Zinedine Zidane","emoji":"🎩","tagline":"The Gliding Maestro","key":"zidane","description":"You move through chaos like it's happening in slow motion."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"ahsoka","result_name":"Ahsoka Tano","result_emoji":"🌙","result_data":{"name":"Ahsoka Tano","emoji":"🌙","tagline":"The Untethered Blade","key":"ahsoka","description":"You learned everything the institution had to teach, then discovered its limits and walked your own way — politely, permanently."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"anakin","result_name":"Anakin Skywalker","result_emoji":"☄️","result_data":{"name":"Anakin Skywalker","emoji":"☄️","tagline":"The Chosen Storm","key":"anakin","description":"You were built with more horsepower than anyone around you — more talent, more feeling, more need — and you've never once done anything halfway."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"boba","result_name":"Boba Fett","result_emoji":"🎯","result_data":{"name":"Boba Fett","emoji":"🎯","tagline":"The Silent Contract","key":"boba","description":"You say maybe ten words a day and let your reputation handle the rest of the conversation."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"c3po","result_name":"C-3PO","result_emoji":"🫖","result_data":{"name":"C-3PO","emoji":"🫖","tagline":"The Fluent Worrier","key":"c3po","description":"You have a statistic for every danger and a worry for every occasion, and you voice all of them, in order, out loud."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"chewbacca","result_name":"Chewbacca","result_emoji":"🐻","result_data":{"name":"Chewbacca","emoji":"🐻","tagline":"The Growling Guardian","key":"chewbacca","description":"You skip the grand speeches and go straight to the deeds: the dawn airport run, the quiet fix, the standing directly between your people and trouble."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"finn","result_name":"Finn","result_emoji":"🤝","result_data":{"name":"Finn","emoji":"🤝","tagline":"The Runaway Hero","key":"finn","description":"You woke up one day inside a life that was wrong for you and did the hardest thing a person can do: you walked."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"han","result_name":"Han Solo","result_emoji":"🎲","result_data":{"name":"Han Solo","emoji":"🎲","tagline":"The Lucky Scoundrel","key":"han","description":"You insist you're only in it for yourself, then keep turning the ship around at exactly the moment it matters."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"kylo","result_name":"Kylo Ren","result_emoji":"🌋","result_data":{"name":"Kylo Ren","emoji":"🌋","tagline":"The Fractured Heir","key":"kylo","description":"You live in the tug-of-war between who you're expected to be and who you actually are, and you feel that tension louder than anyone realizes."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"lando","result_name":"Lando Calrissian","result_emoji":"😎","result_data":{"name":"Lando Calrissian","emoji":"😎","tagline":"The Velvet Gambler","key":"lando","description":"You could sell sand in a desert and leave the buyer feeling like they won."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"leia","result_name":"Princess Leia","result_emoji":"👑","result_data":{"name":"Princess Leia","emoji":"👑","tagline":"The Rebel Heart","key":"leia","description":"You don't wait to be rescued — halfway through, you're usually the one running the rescue."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"luke","result_name":"Luke Skywalker","result_emoji":"🌅","result_data":{"name":"Luke Skywalker","emoji":"🌅","tagline":"The Restless Hope","key":"luke","description":"You grew up staring past the horizon, certain your real life was waiting somewhere beyond it — and unlike most dreamers, you actually went."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"mace","result_name":"Mace Windu","result_emoji":"⚖️","result_data":{"name":"Mace Windu","emoji":"⚖️","tagline":"The Stern Vanguard","key":"mace","description":"You're the one who says the hard no everyone else was avoiding, and you sleep just fine afterward."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"maul","result_name":"Darth Maul","result_emoji":"🗡️","result_data":{"name":"Darth Maul","emoji":"🗡️","tagline":"The Double-Edged Grudge","key":"maul","description":"You were handed a raw deal early, and you converted it into fuel with frightening efficiency."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"obiwan","result_name":"Obi-Wan Kenobi","result_emoji":"🧘","result_data":{"name":"Obi-Wan Kenobi","emoji":"🧘","tagline":"The Civilized Blade","key":"obiwan","description":"You're the one everybody wants in the room when things go wrong: calm, principled, and drier-witted than you get credit for."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"padme","result_name":"Padmé Amidala","result_emoji":"🌷","result_data":{"name":"Padmé Amidala","emoji":"🌷","tagline":"The Steel Rose","key":"padme","description":"You believe in doing things properly — with grace, preparation, and a firm no to anyone who mistakes your kindness for weakness."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"palpatine","result_name":"Emperor Palpatine","result_emoji":"⚡","result_data":{"name":"Emperor Palpatine","emoji":"⚡","tagline":"The Patient Puppeteer","key":"palpatine","description":"You are always playing a longer game than anyone in the room suspects, and you're comfortable waiting years for a plan to ripen."}},{"quiz_type":"starwars","result_key":"poe","result_name":"Poe Dameron","result_emoji":"🚀","result_data":{"name":"Poe Dameron","emoji":"🚀","tagline":"The Daredevil Ace","key":"poe","description":"You operate best just past the edge of what's sensible, and you know it, and you grin about it."}},{"quiz_